<div class="wb_cont_inner"><div id="wb_element_instance14" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><img alt="gallery/IMG_1838 — копия" src="gallery_gen/0b5269f722e4275e2157900abfd2ca38_750x710.PNG"></div><div id="wb_element_instance15" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3">Using text messanger </h3>

<p class="wb-stl-normal"> </p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal">The process of writing text commands to communicate with devices is one of the most native way of communication. That's why text messanger is a great solution for this project. It simple and effective. Telegram can also make it cross-platform.</p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance16" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-power-off" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance17" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance18" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-camera" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance19" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-database" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance20" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;">Main features</h1>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance21" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><img alt="gallery/IMG_2171" src="gallery_gen/319fa0c27abd86443f462fb47c39ef5c_1398.7155963303x1824.0286141535.jpg"></div><div id="wb_element_instance22" class="wb_element wb_element_shape"><a class="wb_shp"></a></div><div id="wb_element_instance23" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,1);">This project is designed to be simple</span></h3>

<p> </p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The major reason of this project being created by me is that I personaly </span></font><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">need it for solving one of my problems:</span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- How not to stand near the 3D printer while it printting  </span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- How to turn it off in case of bad print or when finished</span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- Get photos of the printing process to watch the print   </span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">- Also turn On and Off illumination, because why not      </span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">And this Telegram Bot solved them all! Using Raspbery PI module</span></font></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance24" class="wb_element"><a class="wb_button" href="Contacts/"><span>Contact me if You have any questions</span></a></div><div id="wb_element_instance25" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><b>Power control </b></p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance26" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><b>LED Illumination</b></p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance27" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><b>Photos</b></p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance28" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: center;"><b>History</b></p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance29" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h4 class="wb-stl-pagetitle" style="text-align: center;">Control 3D printer from all over the world</h4>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance30" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom14">There are a lot of things to create for this projects. Not just add more features but also develop better and most efficient way to completely controll 3D printer through the Internet. This is the major task to complete. How to send G-code to the printer through the Internet securely? How to choose the model to print and automatically generate code? And how to do it remotely fast and efficient? This are the most interesting questions to solve. Starting this interesting journey of developing full of new discoveries and experience! </p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance31" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3">So, what's next?</h3>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance32" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-power-off" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance33" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance34" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-camera" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance35" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" title=""><i class="fa fa-database" style="color:#39475d"></i></div><div id="wb_element_instance36" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom14">Turning ON/OFF 3D printer power using relay</p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance37" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom14">LED illumination control </p>
</div><div id="wb_element_instance38" class="wb_element wb_text_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom14">Taking high quality pictures from camera to watch</p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom14">the printing process</p>
